As he saw Marine going to kill Ironraptor he jumped in the way. He 
stuck out his sword to stop Marines weapon. "You shall not kill her 
she is under my protection." He trys to wrap his tentacle around 
Marine to drain the rest of his energy.









[just in case you all want to know Tryeal is 7 foot 5inches tall. He 
is a hooded figure that very few get to see his face. He always has a 
white glow and his sword ad his tentacles are esecially shining. They 
glow white.]
